frames.caption: A majestic city floats above the clouds, its intricate architecture resembling a fortress. The city is perched on a massive rock formation, surrounded by a surreal landscape of swirling mist and golden skies.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical city suspended in the sky, suggesting a dreamlike or otherworldly setting. The city is built on a large, rocky platform, with towering structures and complex architecture.

frames.caption: A massive, ancient ship hovers ominously in a stormy sky, surrounded by swirling clouds. The vessel appears weathered and abandoned, with its towering structure partially obscured by mist.
frames.description: The scene depicts a large, floating ship in a turbulent, cloudy atmosphere, suggesting a fantastical or post-apocalyptic setting.

frames.caption: A misty, mountainous landscape is depicted with ancient, weathered structures carved into the cliffs. The scene is enveloped in a mysterious fog, creating an ethereal atmosphere. The rugged terrain and architectural remnants suggest a forgotten civilization.
frames.description: The scene captures a dramatic and mystical landscape where ancient structures are integrated into steep, rocky cliffs. The fog adds a layer of mystery, hinting at a historical or fantasy setting.
